   "text": "Because they got back to that big statue."
  },
  {
   "start": 577.18,
   "end": 582.62,
   "text": "Figured I'd do a close-up of the statues on it."
  },
  {
   "start": 582.78,
   "end": 586.9,
   "text": "Traveling around, you get an affinity to checking out statues."
  },
  {
   "start": 594.0,
